             was indicted for <rs id="t18000219-55-off331" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000219-55-off331" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000219-55-off331" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000219-55-cd332" type="crimeDate">17th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-55-off331 t18000219-55-cd332"></join>, a great coat, value 10s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000219-55-victim515" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Levy
                        <interp inst="t18000219-55-victim515" type="surname" value="Levy"></interp>
