                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-55-defend513 t18000219-55-punish337"></join>
               publicly whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron HOTHAM.</p>
